  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I mean, the only reason it's of any importance is that-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] first of all, that we saw things and were-- also, the house had to be-- later on, they had to be secured, you know.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to put pails of-- in the attic space, pails of sand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I guess they were preparing, you know, for war or for bombing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And also, of course, we always-- my parents owned the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were I guess 11 apartments.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and we had to always-- on the holidays, we had to put flags out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, my parents, also being Jewish, they still had to put-- you know, buy the flags and put out the appropriate flags, which originally was German flag or Bavarian flag.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I think in the end they had to put out a Nazi flag too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, that was sort of mandated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I've come to a halt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later on, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, there were other apartment-- other apartments in the building.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But later on, when my-- when my father's business began to suffer from the times, there were two rooms in the back that my mother then rented.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had-- we had people renting there and became quite friendly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
